rComments: Really nice and funny prof. There is an attendance sheet and you can only miss a few classes to write the final exam. Little assignments due every Friday and a short quiz but they are really easy. Make sure to study before going to class because you will get called on! Overall enjoyed the course and the group project was a skit that was fun.
